# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# SQL Server 2022 + frms-ops-api — set these in your shell / IDE before
#   cd server/frms-ops-api && mvn spring-boot:run
# Do not commit real passwords. Copy lines you need; remove the leading #.
# Full guide: database/mssql/README.md
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# FRMS_JDBC_URL=jdbc:sqlserver://localhost:1433;databaseName=frms_ops;encrypt=false;trustServerCertificate=true

# Named instance example (adjust instance name):
# FRMS_JDBC_URL=jdbc:sqlserver://localhost\\SQLEXPRESS;databaseName=frms_ops;encrypt=false;trustServerCertificate=true

# TLS + self-signed cert (common on local SQL Server 2022):
# FRMS_JDBC_URL=jdbc:sqlserver://localhost:1433;databaseName=frms_ops;encrypt=true;trustServerCertificate=true

# FRMS_DB_USER=sa
# FRMS_DB_PASSWORD=YourStrong!Passw0rd
